{"tid":327986,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"健身練腳一問","createTime":"2017-07-19T08:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T16:02:50.000Z","uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"868d53972e99ce12f2352d307253cb22caf963ad","tid":327986,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://24.media.tumblr.com/tumblr_m03xqlDGXZ1r7w9n7o1_500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F24.media.tumblr.com%2Ftumblr_m03xqlDGXZ1r7w9n7o1_500.jpg&h=6fd534ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i0.wp.com/www.cyclingtr.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/07thighs1-articleLarge1.jpg?resize=600%2C359\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fwww.cyclingtr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F01%2F07thighs1-articleLarge1.jpg%3Fresize%3D600%252C359&h=bd956b69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依種大腿個練法應該點練？<br />\n除左大之外，佢地仲可以連爆3分幾鐘，抗乳酸既能力仲大過健美個d每組12下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但爆發力應該都好撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，架單車要短時間由0爆上70km/hr需要既爆發力，唔會差得過舉重撚/健力撚<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打知，究極佢地對大腿咁撚癲，係咪每日都要leg day先做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上午squat完、下午練車，再加飲食，日復日咁堅持。最後就出到咁既大腿？<br />\n但香港健身撚最多一星期2次 leg day，因為要復原<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但班痴線佬應該日日都操爆對腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 照理佢地藥檢一定好嚴<br />\n<br />\n健身撚所認識48-72小時大肌肉復原期，其實講緊普通人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有運開動既人，復原期係咪會隨運動年資增高而變短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c4462e2310bbd0422dc4148cd5d4a75bedc37f","tid":327986,"uid":87276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:25:52.000Z","msg":"呢d唔單止係做尖做番黎<br />\n或者可以話單靠尖係練唔到<br />\n你去運動場睇下田徑人點練可略知一二"},{"pid":"a9de6d614c622c65dc0be968a625ad1206e406aa","tid":327986,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:36:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢d唔單止係做尖做番黎<br />\n或者可以話單靠尖係練唔到<br />\n你去運動場睇下田徑人點練可略知一二</blockquote><br />\n但mass上，場地單車對腳真係追得住健美冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇佢地做gym，舉d重量又可以追住健力撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實係咪代表人類可日日leg day<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n田徑個d，我所知追求既野同健力健美好唔同，講協調多"},{"pid":"9eddf18f87e1fe966cb7c3dcf775ac3b57f87660","tid":327986,"uid":87276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T15:11:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢d唔單止係做尖做番黎<br />\n或者可以話單靠尖係練唔到<br />\n你去運動場睇下田徑人點練可略知一二</blockquote><br />\n但mass上，場地單車對腳真係追得住健美冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇佢地做gym，舉d重量又可以追住健力撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實係咪代表人類可日日leg day<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n田徑個d，我所知追求既野同健力健美好唔同，講協調多</blockquote><br />\n田徑人腳力大過健美人絕對唔奇<br />\n你估隻腳無力會跑得快咩<br />\n佢地有專業團隊設計programme訓練<br />\n又有團隊同高科技幫手抒緩疲勞<br />\n又用田徑運動員為例，就算佢地一星期有成六日操練<br />\n佢地都係禁過<br />\n禁講話可以日日legday都合理<br />\n不過要有頂級運動員體質同有專業團隊幫手"},{"pid":"39c88ef94874bb85b566d86794c3cbe00df14ed3","tid":327986,"uid":12458,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T16:02:50.000Z","msg":"其實唔算特別勁 0-70km 有做開gym 識leg press同squat 一星期練1-3日 已經差唔多做到0-70km 爆發力當然要練 但難度屬中等"}]}